  * I promised a samba-print.tar.gz exmaple file, but forgot to include
    one
  * get permissions in /etc right
  * small fix to mknfsroot script.

 -- joost witteveen <joost@rulcmc.leidenuniv.nl>  Sun, 29 Sep 1996 23:36:52 +0200

